history.text: I think that you should see the new Wonder Woman movie if you haven't seen it yet. I don't even like superhero movies that much and It though that it was really good.
It has gotten really great reviews. Including the ones featured on Rotten Tomatoes. 92% and average of 7.6. It is set during World War 1. Great period piece about super heroes.

I hope that you give it a chance it has a great plot and doesn't seem too long. It is the perfect length and features some of the most interesting characters that I have seen in a superhero movie in years.

It is much better than some of the other Marvel movies. I would say that it is better than most. I do like Gaurdians of the Galaxy. I would put it up there with that.
It's really almost a war movie. Which is strange. It is also good to see a character that we haven't seen a million times. It is by far the best DC movie that they have made.
